{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"f6ad7cde9e966530","x":-2400,"y":-160,"width":1170,"height":493,"color":"5","type":"group","label":"Architecture"},
		{"id":"8f51f42444b8a208","type":"text","text":"Claude Skills and backend for capturing day to day notes and activities.\n","x":-20,"y":-420,"width":250,"height":103},
		{"id":"f403e0f82fa9b118","type":"text","text":"Notes still obsidian based","x":-22,"y":-273,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"87cc15ea4352b057","type":"text","text":"Rationale:  Spending too much time making a working markdown editor...","x":400,"y":-293,"width":250,"height":101},
		{"id":"c5ee91f94076ca3d","type":"text","text":"PDQ III","x":-540,"y":-160,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"38902858d2d7eb69","type":"text","text":"Direct commands","x":-22,"y":-145,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"57d6537bcff67ed6","type":"text","text":"With OpenClaw scheduled tasks for managing notes and gathering information...","x":400,"y":-420,"width":250,"height":90},
		{"id":"246204bacb05bd74","type":"text","text":"`/pdq:now` - captures the current meeting from google calender (using google skills), opens a meeting note in obsidian with the details populated.","x":399,"y":140,"width":251,"height":180},
		{"id":"3945aabd7c04c32c","type":"text","text":"Skills","x":-22,"y":290,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"14e7aa61bcb258ea","type":"text","text":"`/pdq:q` - ask a question in the vault.\nUse with `/btw` to not effect context of session.","x":760,"y":-253,"width":250,"height":123},
		{"id":"efb5e4a61f2bd56b","type":"text","text":"Indirect command:  open and apply to template...","x":782,"y":149,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"b7a3bde5473a17f8","type":"text","text":"`/pdq:u <some text>` - records as a new unique note in the configured vault with working context.","x":760,"y":-112,"width":250,"height":112},
		{"id":"15c4d96aefb6cc85","type":"text","text":"`/pdq:summarise` - ","x":396,"y":351,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"27d633a7d13f4550","type":"text","text":"`/pdq:organise <file name>` - triggers the processing pipeline for the file.  ER, Update to summary files, linking and filing.\nUsed by a scheduled ralph loop on the inbox once/night.","x":394,"y":445,"width":250,"height":195},
		{"id":"ef7f55ba5c38ebc6","type":"text","text":"May require a HITL?","x":766,"y":440,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"45fe1e8a3e6681d3","type":"text","text":"Bunch of indirect commands:\n- Entity extraction\n- ER\n- Entity summary and history updates.\n- etc.","x":766,"y":528,"width":250,"height":225},
		{"id":"8449c2bafb2c4307","type":"text","text":"`/pdq:breadcrumbs`","x":394,"y":920,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"d9e984b0ca80a8c4","type":"text","text":"`/pdq:mr` Summarises the current working branch into the configured vault with working context.","x":400,"y":0,"width":250,"height":120},
		{"id":"8585d9cb93e62039","type":"text","text":"CLI","x":-604,"y":471,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"b2534cd9a173bd58","type":"text","text":"`ralph` - run a rw loop using a specified prompt with provided arguments.","x":-940,"y":720,"width":250,"height":113},
		{"id":"1467b0e0fa52ae8a","type":"text","text":"`now` - be for the now skill","x":-660,"y":720,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"7b225c6d4ee43001","type":"text","text":"`mcp` - MCP server for claude - exposes the commands and skills into code.","x":-361,"y":724,"width":250,"height":109},
		{"id":"0f1d52e5ccae0b59","type":"text","text":"`context` - return the current working context as JSON.","x":-43,"y":731,"width":250,"height":69},
